import Navbar from './components/Navbar'
import Hero from './components/Hero'
import { BrowserRouter, Route, Routes } from 'react-router-dom'
import '../src/App.scss'
function App() {
  return (
    <BrowserRouter>
      <Routes>
        <Route path='/' element={<Navbar />} />
        <Route path='/' element={<Hero />} />
      </Routes>
    </BrowserRouter>
  )
}

export default App
